quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,44,WE NADA ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI ‘ESHABE EN-NARI ‘EN KAD WEXHEDNA MA WE’ADENA REBBUNA HEKKÆN FEHEL WEXHEDTUM MA WE’ADE REBBUKUM HEKKÆN KALU NE’AM FE’EDHDHENE MU’UEDHDHINUN BEJNEHUM ‘EN LA’NETU ELLAHI ‘ALA EDH-DHALIMINE
  7,45,EL-LEDHINE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE JEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI KAFIRUNE
  7,46,WE BEJNEHUMA HIXHABUN WE ‘ALEL-’A’RAFI RIXHALUN JA’RIFUNE KULLÆN BISIMAHUM WE NADEW ‘ESHABEL-XHENNETI ‘EN SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM LEM JEDHULUHA WE HUM JETMA’UNE
  7,47,WE ‘IDHA SURIFET ‘EBSARUHUM TILKA’E ‘ESHABI EN-NARI KALU REBBENA LA TEXH’ALNA ME’AL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  7,48,WE NADA ‘ESHABUL-’A’RAFI RIXHALÆN JA’RIFUNEHUM BISIMAHUM KALU MA ‘EGNA ‘ANKUM XHEM’UKUM WE MA KUNTUM TESTEKBIRUNE
  7,49,‘EHA’UULA’L-LEDHINE ‘EKSEMTUM LA JENALUHUMU ELLAHU BIREHMETIN EDHULUL-XHENNETE LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJKUM WE LA ‘ENTUM TEHZENUNE
  7,50,WE NADA ‘ESHABU EN-NARI ‘ESHABEL-XHENNETI ‘EN ‘EFIDU ‘ALEJNA MINEL-MA’I ‘EW MIMMA REZEKAKUMU ELLAHU KALU ‘INNALL-LLAHE HERREMEHUMA ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE
  7,51,EL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU DINEHUM LEHWEN WE LA’IBÆN WE GARRET/HUMUL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA FALJEWME NENSAHUM KEMA NESU LIKA’E JEWMIHIM HADHA WE MA KANU BI’AJATINA JEXHHEDUNE